{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4465be004c","title":"中央和中央文革首长接见西藏军区在京常委时的谈话记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"01b253c785","index":0,"year":1968,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"4465be004c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69fc579f86","type":"title","text":"中央和中央文革首长接见西藏军区在京常委时的谈话记录","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"358ed1524e","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：中央首长有总理、伯达、康生、江青、文元、富治、永胜、法宪、叶群、东兴、玉成。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9bf5f326dd","type":"paragraph","text":"军区在京常委有曾雍雅、任荣、陈明义、赵文进、王亢、吕义山、廖步云、阴法唐同志。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08d625f96c","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：1968年8月26日下午9时25分至11时10分。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b3bd78819","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：人民大会堂东大厅。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b13ac29c4d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天主要是接见群众，听听群众的意见，文化大革命以来未接见他们，心里有些不安，常委内对有些问题认识还不一致，在这里谈清楚，不然在群众中不好谈。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dcc7250a49","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：接到报告20多天后，看到一个宣传提纲，其他地方都未搞宣传提纲，对几个问题的看法不一致，内部很紧张，阴法唐同志很坚持他的意见，说你们几个（指军区党委）是机会主义，手软。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04925b7c1b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：说你们手软，我看你们对阴法唐同志的错误是手软的。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"387d2d36cd","type":"paragraph","text":"当汇报到军队内部打人时","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f3dd68c18","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：把于一星打死了，这是严重的。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb8e9c5889","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到军区8月20日向中央报告的电报时","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db2d8dd090","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你（指阴法唐同志）敢不敢在群众大会上检讨？阴：我敢在群众面前检讨。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87e004a4ec","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：你是不是要在群众大会上示威？！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2e06b724d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：部队出兵，内部打人，还说人家是反革命事件，对不同观点就镇压。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d6db95224","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：打死人，还说人家是反革命！？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9d344c15a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要在群众中见面，实际上是想用多数压少数。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc9a2dd0ea","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到交通厅军管会被赶时","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6ef4911d4","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：支一派、压一派，就被赶出来了。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8ab4406cf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：请阴法唐同志讲一讲，叫阴法唐回去，我们很奇怪，为什么叫他回去呢？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8b18fb17b","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到大昭寺情况时。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b75a46ecee","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：错误的思想，看问题的方法也是错误的，主席很注意大昭寺问题。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ccd84dcc9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：去年1、2月支持“造总”时间短，去年压“大联指”时间短，也未抓他的人，和2、3月不一样，西藏有一个很大的特点，还未抓到一个敌人，新疆还知道一些敌人。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76d03b4e0c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：西藏还有国际间谍，还未搞出来。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30ea718aa1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：对大昭寺事件，你（指阴法唐同志）说清楚一点，不要含糊，要看效果。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95fcd31d49","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你（对阴法唐同志说）对大昭寺事件，由于立场的不同，你认为没有军区布置，但打死人是很严重的，你的思想没完全弄清楚，我们认为严重，你认为不严重。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"141e53d4a3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：石伴樵被抓走，是否他自己搞圈套？","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1089cb8a73","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：\t军区有些干部，反军区党委右倾，主要是他们未压“造总”，部队要有组织纪律嘛，把后勤部副部长打死了，又打伤了冯锦国、郑万兴，部队无组织无纪律，这怎么能行！","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d2a59425d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：是不是开展“四大”的单位？","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"649b48c8a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（答：不是的。）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82ac6754b5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不开展“四大”，更不能允许这样。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e05491a577","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这样怎么能行呢？","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a69d67fdf","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：就是叛国投敌要判死刑的，也应该依法处理，不能随便打死，就是反革命杀人放火的，也要有证据，报告上级才能抓，在边疆少数民族地区，更不应该这样。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cf3706ac9","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：部队无组织无纪律，为什么中央的话都不听？在京常委告诉你们不能出兵，还出兵压“造总”，根本不听中央的话！","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a57c5f09ac","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们的中心问题还是政治不挂帅，敌人就是希望你们这样乱。如果敌人一来，看你们怎么办？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc4815aeb4","type":"paragraph","text":"当阴法唐同志讲有组织错误，也有政治错误时","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dbfd03bcb5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：主要是政治错误，十一中全会文件李井泉不传达，李大章传达了几句，国华同志还不错，支持了“造总”派，8条、10条、“9·5”讲话、“9·26”讲话、主席视察、林副主席讲话，你们宣传是不够的。“7·3”“7·24”布告宣传虽比较好，但大学习、大宣传还不够，部队是很好的，是有功的。广大指战员是好的。你们纠缠在派性的争论，你们的政治领导是很差的。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e8967f808","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：亚东跑的什么人？是你们法院副院长，证明政治工作是很差的。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfc4d59537","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：对无产阶级文化大革命的认识，是比较落后的。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96d5b6b6c1","type":"paragraph","text":"永胜：对中央指示学习差，边疆远，客观上也受限制。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"246c249f18","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：主要是主观努力不够。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f69805528d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把“大联指”小报发到连队，哪有这样的政治工作，全国哪里有？！","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc33d97f69","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：全国只有一个。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"23294486f7","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到报社群众对部队有意见时","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ab469733b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：出报不？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"580ccd5b53","type":"paragraph","text":"文元：很长时间不出报了。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a0724d6e0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理、康生：要很快解决出报问题，不然，怎么能成立革委会？","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cee6770da9","type":"paragraph","text":"当谈到群众自动撤枪时","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7920cc8bf8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军区领导内部团结未解决，应该解决，群众情绪很好。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86986bc515","type":"paragraph","text":"法宪：藏族的同志表现是好的，主动把枪送交军管会，联指头头乱用藏族搞武斗。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a1e4f8300","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：两派都是一样，都有坏人。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea8879768d","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：苗丕一是干什么的？态度怎么样，支持那一派的？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"035a892b01","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们的问题还是领导问题，军管会、警司、军区。军队同志要揑得拢，首先是常委，你们这样涣散，容易出乱子，各行其是，未经批准就出动7个连这样能行吗？","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40284dd022","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：常委根据中央精神发电报，都也不听。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a38e6da112","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：军队自己打自己，都赖在群众身上，我想不通。那天冯锦国讲被打，打的对不对，你们未表态。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6a05098f0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们常委要坚强，外部有敌人，内部也有敌人，你们应在毛泽东思想红旗下团结一致，中央是信任你们的，委托你们任务重大，你们搞不好怎么行？你们好好开两天会，告诉军委办事组派人参加。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c926eb084d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：军队问题还是在内部谈。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4465be004c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}